track_notes: Just beacause the slope is hard; the place is fine, you can park at the village Tourettes du Chateau, the is some place on summit for antenna. the sight is fine from the summit. Have to go back by the same path

This is the long way to the summit, starting from Le Villard (only one car for parking) on the main road. The track is ok, but it can be very warm in summertime; get some more water than usual. Enought room on summit for vertical or small dipole.
